fields.name: Body Power SP.IC20 Indoor Studio Cycle
fields.description: Stylish and sturdy, the Body Power SP.IC20 Indoor Studio Cycle is a high performance studio bike designed to take your home cardio training up a level. Features a heavy 20kg flywheel, tension control resistance, LCD monitor, tablet holder, water bottle holder plus free water bottle.

fields.name: Jordan Fitness 6kg Cast Iron Kettlebell
fields.description: Upgrade your functional training equipment with the 6kg Jordan Cast Iron Kettlebells, manufactured with a high-grade matte powder coated finish and a smooth one-piece design

fields.name: Body Power 65Kg Olympic Dumbbell Set
fields.description: This 65Kg Olympic Dumbbell Set comprises 2 x Olympic Dumbbell handles, Olympic Spring Collars, 8 x 5Kg, 4 x 2.5Kg and 4 x 1.25Kg machine finished Cast Iron Olympic Discs.

fields.name: Body Power 85Kg Cast Iron TRI-GRIP Olympic Weight Set (6ft Bar)
fields.description: The Body Power 85Kg TRI-GRIP Olympic Weight Set features a 6ft Chrome 320kg rated Olympic Bar that is perfect for strength training.

fields.name: Bowflex Xtreme 2 SE Home Gym
fields.description: The Bowflex SE 2 Home Gym delivers a total body workout in a space-efficient, all-in-one package. Features revolutionary no-change cable pulley system providing over 70 exercises. Solid construction with ergonomic, adjustable seat.

fields.name: BH Fitness Pioneer R3 Folding Treadmill
fields.description: Part of BH Fitness’s Pioneer Series, the Pioneer R3 is a stable and secure treadmill that’s ideal for those looking to take up walking or jogging at home. Features include a 6-elastomer damping system, a 2.75 CV motor, 18km/h top speed and 12 pre-set programmes.

fields.name: BH Fitness MYCRON C170 Cross Trainer with I-Concept Technology
fields.description: Ideal for regular use in any home gym environment, the BH Fitness Mycron C170 Cross Trainer features 24 intensity levels, a 43.5cm stride, Bluetooth and telemetric heart rate monitoring, 12 pre-set programmes and iConcept for access to your favourite fitness apps.

fields.name: JOMA WOMEN'S RECORD II VEST (YELLOW)
fields.description: This particular running vest is also available in other colors; it is part of the Record II range made by Joma. The Joma range includes high manufactured and good quality goods that feature that latest sportswear technology such as DRY MX which will assist you throughout your exercise sessions to enable you to be the best you can be!

fields.name: JOMA GIRLS (KIDS) VEST (GREEN)
fields.description: If your child takes part in regular exercise then this piece of running clothing, then why not order this running vest, which will help your child to become the best they can be! Including all the latest sportswear technology, this will contribute to your optimum performance level. Also, to help with performance polyester has been used throughout this vest which is a lightweight material enabling a loose fit, to increase breathability and to maintain a low temperature.

fields.name: NEW BALANCE MEN’S BLACK IMPACT RUN 5 INCH SHORTS
fields.description: Produced using NB Dry technology, these exercise shorts for men are sure to keep you feeling cool and fresh due to the moisture wicking properties of the tech. Sweat is transported away from the surface of the skin and passed through the pants so that it can dry at an express rate from the outer layer.

fields.name: NEW BALANCE MEN’S BLUE IMPACT RUN T-SHIRT
fields.description: Step into summer with a vibrant training kit by ordering this bright blue training jersey today. Printed on the left-hand side of the chest is the New Balance logo and additional branding is seen to the rear of the neck.

fields.name: NEW BALANCE WOMEN’S ACCELERATE COLORBLOCK TIGHTS
fields.description: Creating a Colorblock effect, these navy tights are decorated with bright blue and grey stripes along the length of the legs to add contrast to an otherwise dark pair of leggings. Completing the appearance of the bottoms, the New Balance logo is printed on the waistband and the inner layer is a bright blue colouring.

fields.name: NEW BALANCE MEN’S R.W.T LIGHTWEIGHT WOVEN JACKET
fields.description:
This New Balance jacket for men has been styled using a colour block appearance. The colours featured on this jacket are dark blue, light sky blue, grey and black which are accompanied by white New Balance branding on the chest and rear of the shoulder.

Ensuring that you remain dry when the weather turns, this jacket has been created using a water-resistant fabric that does not allow the water to permeate through the garment to reach your body. Therefore, you can continue training in comfort no matter the weather by donning this lightweight jacket.

fields.name: NEW BALANCE TENACITY DARK TEAL TRAINING T-SHIRT
fields.description:
Designed in dark teal this men’s training top can be worn as a casual t-shirt or when training in the gym. A crew style neckline provides a modern feel to the t-shirt and the New Balance logo appears in black print on the chest.

The training top is part of New Balance’s athletic range and is made from 100% Polyester that is lightweight and won’t restrict your performance. In addition, NB DRY technology will actively wick sweat and moisture away from the skin so you can concentrate on your performance.

fields.name: Body Power 4ft x 3ft Floor Protector Mat
fields.description: The 48" x 36" (4ft x 3ft) Floor Protector Mat is ideal for protecting your floor when placed beneath Cycles and Compact Elliptical Cross Trainers.

fields.name: Bowflex Bluetooth Heart Rate Armband
fields.description: Less obtrusive than a chest strap, this armband lets you monitor your heart rate while you train. Made from ABS and Leice (Lycra), the armband features a Velcro strap for secure fastening and sweat resistant (IPX – 7), it’s ideal for those intense HIIT sessions. This slim, comfortable armband is a Bluetooth® BLE heart rate device, equipped with an optics sensor that monitors your heart rate

fields.name: Body Power 55cm Gym Ball With Pump (300Kg Burst Resistant) Grey
fields.description: Suitable for a wide range of core, strength, flexibility, preparation and recovery exercises, the Body Power Gym Ball is a must have piece of fitness equipment. Size: 55cm – pump included.

fields.name: Body Power Mini Bands (Set of 4)
fields.description: Add extra resistance to your training with the Body Power Mini Band Set of 4, featuring four colour coordinated bands from Light to Extra Heavy.

fields.name: Body Power Hydration Water Bottle
fields.description: Stay hydrated with our new 520ml Body Power Hydration Water Bottle, completely BPA free and finishes with a smart black and red design and for essential hydration on the go.

fields.name: Fitness-MAD Hi-Speed 2 way Power Pump
fields.description: 2-way hi-pressure Swiss Ball pump This pump makes blowing up a Swiss ball a breeze with two-way action for faster inflation

fields.name: Reebok Step
fields.description: Ideal for home gyms and studio workout environments, the Reebok Step is the perfect HIIT companion. Height adjustable, users can customise the intensity of workouts, and store it away easily.

fields.name: Protein Brownie (box of 12)
fields.description:
With up to 75% less sugar than standard supermarket alternatives, enjoy an afternoon pick-me-up without ruining all your hard-earned progress.

Created with heaps of delicious cocoa powder and baked with sweet chocolate chips, our Protein Brownies are packed with 23g of protein for an indulgent everyday treat.

fields.name: Vegan Vitamin D3 Softgels
fields.description: Plant-based sunshine vitamin, for everyday wellbeing — whatever the weather

fields.name: Creatine Monohydrate Tablets
fields.description: Getting creatine from your diet alone can be difficult as it’s mainly found in meat and fish — these tablets provide a quick way to hit your daily requirements without the fuss of meal prep, plus they’re vegetarian-friendly.

fields.name: Pure Caffeine Tablets
fields.description:
A popular pre-workout ingredient, our Pure Caffeine tablets deliver a boost of caffeine — to power you through even the toughest of workouts.

Caffeine helps to improve endurance performance and capacity, so you can get the most from every session and push past your limits.

fields.name: All-Natural Peanut Butter
fields.description:
Created with a blend of roasted brown peanuts, our Crunchy Peanut Butter is all-natural and a great source of protein — ideal for supporting your training and curbing your cravings.

Plus, it’s free from added salt, sugar, palm oil, and preservatives, while being packed with fibre and the essential nutrients vitamin E and magnesium, this super-nutritious snack is the sweet and simple way to keep your training on track.

fields.name: Vegan Protein Blend
fields.description: Completely free from artificial colours and flavours, our all-natural Vegan Protein Powder is a blend of pea and fava bean protein isolates, to enhance your plant-powdered diet. Oh, and it’s low in sugar and delicious too.

fields.name: 20 Minute Toning Body Workout for Women
fields.description: This toning body workout for women is specifically designed for women but can also be followed along by men of course.  It consists of 15 different body toning exercises with weights (in the form of dumbbells, but you can use water bottles etc. if you like)

fields.name: Ultimate Pilates Toning Workout | 30 Minutes Abs, Glutes, Back
fields.description: Here's your ultimate 30 minute Pilates workout as part of the 2 week pilates challenge calendar. The routine is the ultimate pilates abs, glutes, back and waist workout and will work on toning and lengthening from head to toe but also keep your pilates posture and form.

fields.name: Glutes, Thighs, and Abs, Toning Workout
fields.description: Tighten and tone your butt and legs with this no-equipment workout from Victoria's Secret model trainer Stephen Pasterino. His P.Volve method focuses on building long, lean muscle tone and eliminating bulk...

fields.name: 30 MIN ARMS & ABS WORKOUT || At-Home Pilates
fields.description: Work your arms & abs with this 30 Minute Dynamic Pilates Workout! All you need is a set of light hand weights (I'm using 1kg weights) or you can get creative and use household items, e.g. canned foods or water bottles.

fields.name: 30 Minute Beginner Weight Training for Beginners
fields.description: 30 Minute Beginner Weight Training for Beginners - Home Strength Training Full Body Dumbbell Workout instructions

fields.name: Total Body Strength Training Without Weights for Women
fields.description: Strength Training does not mean lifting weights! You CAN strength train using only your BODYWEIGHT. This workout is low impact and great for beginners too.

fields.name: 20 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT With Weights
fields.description: Full body exercises to get you sweating and muscles burning in only 20 MINUTES! This home strength workout uses 2 sets of dumbbells, but you can use whatever you have available to you at home!

fields.name: Killer FULL BODY Workout // Strength Workout
fields.description: Burn fat + build strength with this Full Body Strength Workout - from home or the gym! (I'm using a set of 10lb weights + a 25lb dumbbell)

fields.name: Full body HIIT Workout with Weights
fields.description: 30 exercises in 30 minutes in this No Repeat workout. We are targeting the full body with today's HIIT workout and we are using weights to increase the intensity, burn fat and build strength!

fields.name: 20 Min Home Strength Workout for Men & Women at Home
fields.description: The #1 Home Strength Training Workout with motivational trainer Coach Kozak. This total body dumbbell workout for men and for women will push and challenge you to new limits.

fields.name: 30-Minute HIIT Cardio Workout with Warm Up
fields.description: In this high intensity cardio bodyweight workout from trainer Lita Lewis, you’ll spike your heart rate with high-knees, fast feet, and star jumps; plus work your core and lower body with jumping lunges and planks - at home! No equipment needed!

fields.name: 30 MIN CALORIE KILLER HIIT Workout
fields.description: Here's a killer post-Christmas Cookie Burner workout for you all! Time to get the heart pumping, burn some calories and sweat it out. Grab your mat, a bottle of water and let's do it team!

fields.name: INTENSE FULL BODY CRUSHER - HIIT WORKOUT
fields.description:
30 Minute Bodyweight Only Workout (No Equipment needed) - No Repeat - Stronger Together!
Tabata is an advanced level of the workout and is not suitable for beginners. If you are a newbie start with simple and easy exercise before attempting Tabata. Performing Tabata, in the beginning, might strain your muscles and you may get injured.

fields.name: 15 MIN BEGINNER CARDIO Workout
fields.description: Do this 15 minute beginner, full body, cardio workout at home! This is a non-stop cardio routine with basic, low impact exercises for beginners. No equipment needed. Just yourself!

fields.name: 30-Minute Standing Cardio Workout
fields.description: Get your heart rate up without taking it to the mat with this standing cardio workout that you can do anywhere! These cardio exercises will jump-start your endurance and leave every muscle worked!

fields.name: 25 minute interval cardio workout
fields.description: In this short interval cardio workout - Daniel Bartlett of Body Project takes you through a series of combination cardio exercises that will get your heart rate high and turn your Body into a calorie and fat burning machine.

fields.name: Low impact cardio workout for ALL fitness levels
fields.description: At home cardio workout with Team Body Project, Daniel and Alexandra Bartlett. Includes warm up and cool down.
